=Directory of Sustainable Manufacturing queries==

Available from James Gien Wong:


==Criteria==

- The critical selection factors have been

    - lowest cost / highest reliability
    - durable
    - easy maintenance
    - can be open sourced
    - can be manufactured cosmolocally via community production cooperatives
    - scaleable cosmolocally
    - aligned with open source circular economy
    - low embedded energy costs
    - fits holistically and synergistically with other technologies I've sourced for a holistic system design for: 
        - residential home system
        - neighbourhood ( up to a dozen residential homes sharing common resource infrastructure that makes sense
        - community scale ( hundreds of homes to thousands)
        - cities
    - DIY
    - modular
    - fits within cross-scale translated, earth system boundaries for just and safe transition "


